{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-7","id":"msg_011NtvfEWc9iAHahPzarKsrk","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01FGNtYCoGCbrtrCGi33Akhf","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/tmp/fdb-0.7.0-PVQ-P1-DESIGN-20260527T132416Z/dev/design/0.7.0-vector-quant-pack1.md","old_string":"- The Pack 1 migration preserves the `rowid <-> write_cursor`\n  identity used throughout the writer loop (`lib.rs:2174-2175`\n  comment, `:2177`, `:2181`, `:2265`); the `INSERT INTO\n  vector_default_v2 ... SELECT v.rowid` clause is explicit\n  about it.","new_string":"- The Pack 1 migration preserves the `rowid <-> write_cursor`\n  identity by JOIN-ing `vector_default.rowid` into the staging\n  table (D4 sub-step 1: `SELECT v.rowid, v.embedding, r.kind\n  FROM vector_default v JOIN _fathomdb_vector_rows r ON r.rowid\n  = v.rowid`) and then repopulating the recreated\n  `vector_default` with the same staged rowids (D4 sub-step 3:\n  `INSERT INTO vector_default(rowid, ...) SELECT s.rowid, ...\n  FROM _fathomdb_vector_migration_v0_7_0 s`); the writer-loop\n  pins at `lib.rs:2174-2175`, `:2177`, `:2181`, `:2265` continue\n  to hold."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1700,"cache_read_input_tokens":50295,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1700},"output_tokens":54,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5e259876-f4b4-41bd-a27c-d31853bc06c1","uuid":"c19c7e06-38cc-4c11-b0fd-a3317be5eb2f","request_id":"req_011CbTBwvZ9EcWPr6DtiXHH5"}
